Date: Mon, 7 Jul 2025 16:19:18 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 14/24] QSDK:CP:wifi:ath12K: send assoc and deassoc events to
 userspace

Implement association and deassociation events to notify vendor
applications of the changes. Add vendor app callback functions
to handle these events.

Patch-dependency:
0462-13-QSDK-CP-wifi-ath12K-send-app-initialization-response.patch

Signed-off-by: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Aloka Dixit <aloka.dixit@oss.qualcomm.com>
